data.description:
Come see this well maintained, brick beauty, move in ready home!
With its modern touches, curb appeal, and spacious layout, this home has everything you are looking for! Conveniently situated in the sought-after Pebble Hills neighborhood.  This appealing residence offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an accommodating living area with a fireplace, and a bonus room that gives you that additional living space! Enjoy refrigerated A/C that will keep you cool in the summer.
With an impeccable low maintenance front landscape, plenty of parking space, privacy wall, and a spacious backyard ready to be customized to your lifestyle. Don't hesitate and call to schedule a showing TODAY!
